Rating: 4
As this is a bisque, I felt there was a step missing so I tweaked it. After simmering the veggies down in the tomato, broth & wine, strain it through a sieve and puree the solids in a food processor. Then add the mixture back into the broth & proceed as directed. Absolute Heaven! This is one of my favorites, now & for years to come!

